									<p>He is posted as Assistant Audit Officer at the office of the Deputy Director, State Audit at Andhra University and at present is undergoing training at the Dr. MCR MHRD Institute, Hyderabad.</p>

									<p>In the UPSC Civil Services Examination 2009, Mr. Pawan Kumar has secured 145th rank and thus became the first civil servant to have qualified for five JRFs.</p>

